<h1>Rural Grocery Initiative</h1>

<p>
    <br />
    The mission of the <a href="https://www.ruralgrocery.org/" target="_blank">Rural Grocery Initiative</a> (RGI) is to provide resources
    to help sustain and enhance independently-owned rural grocery stores. RGI, a program supported by K-State Research and
    Extension, assists communities and citizens to strengthen rural grocery operations and improve access to healthy foods.
</p>

